{"tid":1593473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主線支線任務同時做有機會係失敗原因?","createTime":"2019-09-25T05:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T05:46:57.000Z","uid":30774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b503e04709f52f1ba3f09f7766886cc3fdd1b1","tid":1593473,"uid":30774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMkGyrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMkGyrn.jpg&h=f1d45306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前要做到遍地開花，平日幾條支線的確係可以成功帶入社區。但星期六日嘅主線係唔會有支線分薄人流。<br />\n<br />\n反觀而家星期六日嘅主線（和你塞，大遊行）都係有其他支線分薄人流，和你塞已經兩個星期被德福同新城市行動完全帶走咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放映會 罷買呢啲重要過集會遊行?<br />\n<br />\n929 唔希望大家走曬去又一城 <br />\n另外10.1不如取消塞機場集中火力去維園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3b4e8dec451e1662aa4be26eff8af12b483f2cdc","tid":1593473,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"a68305b1d687ea8e4f1ff43128a6daf5879d1277","tid":1593473,"uid":30774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"742d6d509350e6317d073380b27c1abefb176030","tid":1593473,"uid":30774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:45:16.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"11937eec25a7e5a77141976c4f93b7137b26509b","tid":1593473,"uid":30774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"bc2efb9a9be097201e52e226cf65422278d44306","tid":1593473,"uid":30774,"lik